text: Champigny en Rochereau is a commune in the department of Vienne, western France. The municipality was established on 1 January 2017 by merger of the former communes of Champigny-le-Sec (the seat) and Le Rochereau.Arrêté préfectoral 19 July 2016 == See also == *Communes of the Vienne department == References == Category:Communes of Vienne
title: Champigny en Rochereau
